[BOTH LAUGHING]

1027
01:10:12.187 --> 01:10:14.689
[EMMA RETCHING
AND COUGHING]

1028
01:10:18.493 --> 01:10:22.664
Think it was the fish?
It smelled a little weird.

1029
01:10:30.472 --> 01:10:33.541
You think maybe you're pregnant?

1030
01:10:33.541 --> 01:10:35.677
No, I'm not.

1031
01:10:35.677 --> 01:10:39.247
It's not that
I don't want kids, it's just...

1032
01:10:39.247 --> 01:10:40.648
You know...

1033
01:10:40.648 --> 01:10:42.450
I know.

1034
01:10:42.450 --> 01:10:44.086
Yeah.

1035
01:10:44.086 --> 01:10:45.920
You want kids?

1036
01:10:45.920 --> 01:10:48.323
Someday.

1037
01:10:49.757 --> 01:10:51.493
Me too.

1038
01:11:02.104 --> 01:11:06.141
I'd give anything
for some toothpaste right now.

1039
01:11:06.141 --> 01:11:09.311
And some chicken soup
and a sad movie.

1040
01:11:09.311 --> 01:11:13.047
Come here, lie down.
I'll make you feel better.

1041
01:11:20.088 --> 01:11:22.457
Hmm.

1042
01:11:22.457 --> 01:11:26.328
Do you ever think about
what everybody else is doing?

1043
01:11:28.196 --> 01:11:30.798
Who's everybody else?

1044
01:11:30.798 --> 01:11:33.168
Friends, family,

1045
01:11:33.168 --> 01:11:35.370
people out in the world.

1046
01:11:37.339 --> 01:11:41.109
We're everybody else now,
prom queen.

1047
01:11:41.109 --> 01:11:43.678
Ow. What...?

1048
01:11:44.912 --> 01:11:46.848
- What was that?
- What the...?

1049
01:11:46.848 --> 01:11:49.651
[MONKEY GIBBERING]

1050
01:11:56.057 --> 01:11:58.360
Whoa, whoa, whoa.
Okay, buddy.

1051
01:11:58.360 --> 01:11:59.827
Stop, stop.
Okay, put it down.

1052
01:11:59.827 --> 01:12:02.297
Put the gun down
and step away from the vehicle.

1053
01:12:02.297 --> 01:12:04.832
Come on, monkey,
drop the gun.

1054
01:12:04.832 --> 01:12:06.201
[GIBBERING]

1055
01:12:06.201 --> 01:12:09.237
No, no, no. Stop, stop, stop.
Put it down!

1056
01:12:09.237 --> 01:12:10.572
Come on, little guy.

1057
01:12:10.572 --> 01:12:13.575
I'll trade you,
banana for the gun.

1058
01:12:16.110 --> 01:12:18.213
He didn't even take his banana.

1059
01:12:21.283 --> 01:12:22.750
You know what?

1060
01:12:24.519 --> 01:12:26.421
What the hell?
What'd you do that for?

1061
01:12:26.421 --> 01:12:27.822
I don't wanna hope anymore.

1062
01:12:27.822 --> 01:12:30.091
You're acting crazy.
Why did you fire...?

1063
01:12:30.091 --> 01:12:31.493
Oh, I'm crazy?

1064
01:12:31.493 --> 01:12:33.828
No, see, crazy is thinking
we can survive

1065
01:12:33.828 --> 01:12:36.130
for more than a year
on this stupid island.

1066
01:12:36.130 --> 01:12:37.332
That's crazy.

1067
01:12:37.332 --> 01:12:39.066
We're gonna make
a life here, Em.

1068
01:12:39.066 --> 01:12:40.668
It's gonna be better,
I promise.

1069
01:12:40.668 --> 01:12:43.738
No noise. I mean,
what's so good out there anyway?

1070
01:12:43.738 --> 01:12:47.242
Life, Dean. Life is
what's so good out there.

1071
01:12:47.242 --> 01:12:50.878
Our families, our...
Everything.

1072
01:12:53.448 --> 01:12:55.617
You're crazy if you think
for one second

1073
01:12:55.617 --> 01:12:58.052
I would actually choose
to live like this.

1074
01:12:58.052 --> 01:13:00.355
This is not living,
this is surviving.

1075
01:13:20.275 --> 01:13:22.777
Any luck?

1076
