1097
01:14:43.758 --> 01:14:46.093
Hey, get down.
I don't think so.

1098
01:14:46.093 --> 01:14:49.163
REPORTER 1: There's Emma.
REPORTER 2: Emma!

1099
01:14:49.163 --> 01:14:50.565
REPORTER 3:
Hey, Emma!

1100
01:14:50.565 --> 01:14:54.436
