1101
01:14:54.436 --> 01:14:56.571
REPORTER 2: Over here!
REPORTER 4: Emma!

1102
01:14:56.571 --> 01:14:59.341
♪ I still believe

1103
01:14:59.341 --> 01:15:02.176
[CROWD CHATTERING]

1104
01:15:02.176 --> 01:15:03.678
REPORTER 5: Hey, Emma!

1105
01:15:03.678 --> 01:15:07.649
♪ Rolling time may fate me

1106
01:15:09.917 --> 01:15:14.288
♪ Turning gold into gray

1107
01:15:14.288 --> 01:15:17.024
[INDISTINCT DIALOGUE]

1108
01:15:30.605 --> 01:15:35.610
♪ Don't let me miss my cue

1109
01:15:35.610 --> 01:15:39.313
