♪ Leave me as you find me

1116
01:16:05.440 --> 01:16:06.841
Emma!

1117
01:16:06.841 --> 01:16:09.811
[ALL SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY]

1118
01:16:12.847 --> 01:16:16.350
JACK: I never thought
