1120
01:16:26.761 --> 01:16:28.262
- Hey.
- Hey.

1121
01:16:28.262 --> 01:16:29.897
What are you doing here?

1122
01:16:29.897 --> 01:16:33.334
I wanted to check on you,
first night back and all.

1123
01:16:33.334 --> 01:16:36.804
I was just looking
at Facebook and stuff.

1124
01:16:38.139 --> 01:16:40.074
Weird being back, huh?

1125
01:16:40.074 --> 01:16:41.909
Yeah.

1126
01:16:43.277 --> 01:16:46.448
They said we don't have to
go back to school right away.

1127
01:16:46.448 --> 01:16:47.982
Yeah, I know.

1128
01:16:47.982 --> 01:16:51.052
I think I'm gonna go
next week, though,

1129
01:16:51.052 --> 01:16:53.421
get back into it.

1130
01:16:53.421 --> 01:16:54.656
Of course you are.

1131
01:16:54.656 --> 01:16:57.358
What does that mean?

1132
01:16:57.358 --> 01:16:59.861
Nothing, just...

1133
01:16:59.861 --> 01:17:02.196
I guess summer's over, huh?

1134
01:17:02.196 --> 01:17:04.799
You're talking in code.

1135
01:17:07.401 --> 01:17:09.904
My dad told me about your party.

1136
01:17:09.904 --> 01:17:14.008
Mom's throwing it,
a homecoming thing.

1137
01:17:14.008 --> 01:17:15.443
Are you gonna come?

1138
01:17:15.443 --> 01:17:17.411
Lots of kids from school
will be there. It'll be fun.

1139
01:17:17.411 --> 01:17:20.482
Yeah, fun.

1140
01:17:22.750 --> 01:17:25.787
You should probably go.

1141
