1147
01:17:53.715 --> 01:17:56.684
I can't imagine
the courage it took

1148
01:17:56.684 --> 01:17:58.119
to survive those days.

1149
01:17:58.119 --> 01:18:00.087
I really can't.

1150
01:18:00.087 --> 01:18:02.156
But I'm so grateful
that you did.

1151
01:18:02.156 --> 01:18:03.858
To my girl...

1152
01:18:03.858 --> 01:18:05.760
