I can't come. Sorry.

1175
01:19:15.329 --> 01:19:18.065
REPORTER: They're calling it
"the miracle at sea."

1176
01:19:18.065 --> 01:19:20.935
After more than 100 days
stranded on a desert island,

1177
01:19:20.935 --> 01:19:23.738
<i>two high school juniors,
Emmaline Robinson</i>

1178
01:19:23.738 --> 01:19:25.139
<i>and Dean McMullen,</i>

1179
01:19:25.139 --> 01:19:27.108
<i>have safely returned to their school,</i>

1180
01:19:27.108 --> 01:19:29.210
<i>to their family, to their friends,</i>

1181
01:19:29.210 --> 01:19:30.578
<i>to their lives</i>

1182
01:19:30.578 --> 01:19:33.114
<i>that they thought
they might never see again.</i>

1183
01:19:33.114 --> 01:19:35.617
[PEOPLE APPLAUDING
AND CHEERING]

1184
01:19:35.617 --> 01:19:38.219
LIZZIE: Welcome back.

1185
01:19:38.219 --> 01:19:40.755
Excuse us.

1186
01:19:40.755 --> 01:19:43.658
♪ Maybe I needed out

1187
01:19:43.658 --> 01:19:46.894
♪ Maybe I missed a step

