1191
01:20:01.809 --> 01:20:05.246
♪ Come to me now

1192
01:20:05.246 --> 01:20:08.616
♪ It's time to break down

1193
01:20:08.616 --> 01:20:11.719
♪ In the morning

1194
01:20:11.719 --> 01:20:13.454
♪ We will wake up

1195
01:20:13.454 --> 01:20:15.757
I told him
I'd think about it.

1196
01:20:15.757 --> 01:20:17.725
Oh, my God, Em,
you're my hero.

1197
01:20:17.725 --> 01:20:20.394
