01:20:33.007 --> 01:20:35.843
MAN: Hey, McMullen.

1204
01:20:35.843 --> 01:20:38.646
♪ For your love

1205
01:20:38.646 --> 01:20:41.582
MAN: Come on.

1206
01:20:41.582 --> 01:20:44.886
♪ For your love

1207
01:20:45.987 --> 01:20:49.456
♪ Maybe I had my doubt

