01:21:06.040 --> 01:21:09.043
♪ But I still needed you

1214
01:21:10.577 --> 01:21:13.848
♪ This is love now

1215
01:21:13.848 --> 01:21:17.584
♪ Crazy love now

1216
01:21:17.584 --> 01:21:20.087
[PHONE RINGING]

